{"type":null,"faqId":14394,"title":"How do I update my B1's firmware and app versions?","answer":"<p>\n<span><span>Your B1 supports OTA updates. To update your B1's firmware and app, perform the following steps:</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span>Ensure that your B1 is connected to your phone properly over Bluetooth.</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>Run <b>Huawei TalkBand o</b>n your phone and choose <b>Settings</b>&gt;<b>About</b>.</span></span>\n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=47365\">\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>Touch <b>Update</b> <b>TalkBand</b> to update your B1's firmware.</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=47366\"></span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span>4.<span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span>Touch <b>Update TalkBand app</b> to update your Huawei TalkBand app.</span></span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span><span><span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=47367\"></span></span>\n</span></span></p>\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":332,"faqType":"Third-party Applications","useful":38,"unUseful":24,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"6319","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Other-APPs","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1408440339000,"seriesProductName":"B1","visitedTimes":5837,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag